    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s not a view in doctrine bare"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But an unveiling of the Christ."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s marvelous and far beyond"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our mental thought or power to share."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s rich, unlimited, profound,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Immeasurable, and marvelous."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet ’tis a greater wonder still"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He needs heirs of salvation—us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God has accomplished many things—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s planned, created, and brought forth."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Son is now appointed Heir,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Administrator of God’s worth."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But in th’ economy of God"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is not one, but many sons."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "One is the firstborn Son of God"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "With many other living ones."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ will inherit all God’s things,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we’re the heirs of God with Christ."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re growing now to be matured;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As heirs we’ll soon be legalized."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re joint-heirs with the firstborn Son,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Inheriting the universe."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re in this corporation vast—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All partners of Christ and the church."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In spirit, in the church, we see"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our calling of unrivaled worth."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re destined, not to go to heaven."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re destined to be kings on earth."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "8"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re paupers, yet we’re glorious kings."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Inheriting the kingdom vast,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The earth, God’s throne, and e’en all things"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And all the Father is and has."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "9"
    }
  ],
